    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This chassis is paired with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. Technical highlights include recent preventative maintenance on the rod bearings and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension features an aluminum multi-link rear setup and MacPherson struts up front, providing precise turn-in and exceptional feedback. While the exterior shows minor road wear, the drivetrain remains potent, pulling hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with the signature metallic rasp of the factory-tuned exhaust.",
