      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch on the rear passenger door are present upon close inspection\u2014typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with premium leather seats that show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready; it features a complete service log, with a recent synthetic oil change and a fresh set of tires installed last season. The engine runs smooth and quiet, and the transmission shifts effortlessly. This is a reliable, honest car for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean presentation.",
